r />\n就往小路上方逃走。<br />\n<br />\n我極度肯定佢係住喺粉嶺，<br />\n所以再次提醒大家小心呢兩個危險人物，<br />\n如果有人知道佢哋喺邊度出沒,<br />\n或者住喺邊,有任何資料 ，<br />\n請通知我！🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻 thank you !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/tgV6XQZ.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"57914bfd50e60c6e64b94501c69657a26bb71589","tid":2033263,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"40藍絲毀連儂牆打人 警護送搭的士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1817324/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1817324/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200109/VPF4XJM7HVJQ4AT5YLJEPRQVYM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200109%2FVPF4XJM7HVJQ4AT5YLJEPRQVYM%2F&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=2300f8e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200109%2FVPF4XJM7HVJQ4AT5YLJEPRQVYM%2F&h=024ba632\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200109/VPF4XJM7HVJQ4AT5YLJEPRQVYM/</a><br />\n0藍絲毀連儂牆打人 警護送搭的士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】約40名男女昨凌晨持漆鏟及掃帚等，強行清理葵涌梨木樹邨巴士總站連儂牆，更追打街坊，有街坊被打傷。數十名警員到場竟圍着街坊，聲稱未見有人持武，待該批男女清走文宣後，再協助他們截的士離開，無人被捕。事件惹來街坊及區議員怒吼，炮轟警方選擇性執法，「藍絲就揸乜都睇唔到，黃絲就揸支雷射筆都話攻擊性武器！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：200市民悼梓樂逝世兩月 警拘多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200109/large/1578502600_ce66.gif\" />"},{"pid":"9d8e5dded49c49b8f22c7c358c0e4eb232c64c65","tid":2033263,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f27f9e4c5476b6f9358c0c4e18e6088473746d","tid":2033263,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afd991afc6862271ec7d94d39ef3